title: Swing Chick
description:
At the top of the tallest tree in the forest, among the clouds, there was a nest. Once one of the eggs cracked, and from it hatched funny little clumsy chick. He was carefree, and rejoiced bright sunny days. But here was a trouble - a branch broke and the little bird began to fall. He was not yet able to fly, but weak wings allow him to soar gently, with interest examining life on the trunk of a huge tree. Along the way he meets beetles, spiders, dragonflies, ants, huge leaves, and red eyes in the hollow scare. Help little bird avoid sharp branches, and regale tasty worms.

-= How to play =-
- Tap to change direction.
- Eat funny worms for bonus time.
- Avoid sharp branches.

-= Features =-
- Funny Clumsy Chick.
- Eat more worms for the passing game.
- A simple tap on the screen to change direction.
- Amazing cartoon graphics and warm colors.
- It will bring you joy and make you happy.
- More than 5 different kinds of insects.
- Realistic sounds of nature forest.
- Pause function for a comfortable game.
- A fun adventure for children and adults.

Enjoy the game.
